Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界在撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许杀人  不可偷窃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.29,0:00:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得欺瞒  不能奸淫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是谎言  纯粹的欺骗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.57,0:00:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想被杀  不想被窃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才以正义伦理等谎言为盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护弱小的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.35,0:00:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原始的真理是弱肉强食
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞噬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的财富  权力  乃至世界本身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.77,0:00:35.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯吾布列塔尼亚能粉碎世界的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.55,0:00:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带来真实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.47,0:00:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Britannia!…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.38,0:02:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Turn 07\N被丢弃的假面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像做噩梦了  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜…娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…什么都没说  什么都没
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉所期望的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉所选择的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而在那里  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero是个障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉的人身安全已经有所保障
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有布列塔尼亚正规军和朱雀在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是最棘手的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也因此可以信任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  正如我过去所期望的那般
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有我去保护  也已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看  据说这个寺庙是千年前搭建的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管那些啦  你知道水枪在哪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明把大家的份都准备好了的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网、蜡烛、假发、烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有铃鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我们好像是去修学旅行的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧  我这可是第二次了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉无精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:52.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过期待修学旅行导致睡不着觉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…就是这么回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路还真像个小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Area 11新总督即将发表就任致辞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请全体同学到礼堂集合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.68,0:04:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是布列塔尼亚第87皇位继承者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉·Vi·布列塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替日前殉职的卡纳雷斯公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出任本届Area 11总督
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我双目失明且腿脚不便  因此还需各方协助…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总督？那样的小女孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说多多关照…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没搞错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点匆忙  有件事希望大家能协助我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我准备重建「日本行政特区」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:05:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算和这词沾边  也是个禁忌  她竟然还…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:02.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日本特区
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布列塔尼亚人及「Numbers」都将受到平等对待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Eleven」可以重新恢复「日本人」的叫法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她刚才说「日本人」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想再次欺骗我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}没必要以人种为理由  将人与人之间区分开来…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木朱雀也在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他不也是日本人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是杀戮公主的骑士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出卖Zero的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昔日日本特区曾经引发过不幸的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我认为其宗旨并没有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创造平等  温馨的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑之骑士团的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请务必加入日本特区
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承认彼此的错误  一定可以重返正途
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我坚信这点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我吃了一惊啊  娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你会提出重建日本特区
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀  尤菲姐姐想做的事并非错误的  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  错的不是尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\an8}换乘快车的各位乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\an8}请在下车后到站台对面3号线等候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.58,0:06:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\an8}下一站可换乘千京线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\an8}各站停车在5号…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是Zero  还是我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(572,352)\fad(200,200)}Area 11  横须贺港
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个总督也和杀戮公主尤菲米娅一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.83,0:06:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实  日本人恐怕谁也不会参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用甜言蜜语把人引出来后全部杀掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:06:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太看扁我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今后该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是跟布列塔尼亚决战啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的Knight Mare只剩下红莲一架了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我们还有Zero啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如玉城先生所言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  为什么没见到Zero大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得新娘子特地赶来的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在中华联邦之时也是连封信都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会搞外遇去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人  他是骗人的  神乐殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.02,0:07:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  没关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所谓「英雄爱美人」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到成年男人的生理状况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:36.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好  比外表看起来成熟多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在的时候  谢谢你陪伴他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  华莲小姐也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:57.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支持Zero大人的三个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我们是三人官女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}（三人宫女：日本女孩节上装饰用的，位居次层的偶人）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,官女？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀君呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是要追击黑之骑士团  出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精密检查都还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这点真是一点都没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了完成Conquesta
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑麦面包加姜黄和精白糖  芥末酱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是一点都没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  至今为止都是为了娜娜莉而行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}各位  初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}我是布列塔尼亚第87皇位继承者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}娜娜莉·Vi·布列塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}代替日前殉职的卡纳雷斯公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:09:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs23}出任本届Area 11总督
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊  小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉也许已经察觉了我的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此  她还是说要继承尤菲遗志
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此  我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了要先给钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.55,0:09:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了  穷光蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丧家之犬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊  你们不也跟我一样是Area 11人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要这个的话  就拿钱来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布列塔尼亚人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本人吃日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是以「布列塔尼亚人的走狗」之身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说日本人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们才不稀罕布列塔尼亚人的同情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:09:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是Area 11人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生就少管人家的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是自愿为我干活的  学生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我  贱民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我做俯卧撑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科尔查先生  你做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我去跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹲起运动  嚎叫  拍手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回这里也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我而言  重要的是他活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能呢  不做Zero是很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是什么浪漫的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样下去的话  黑之骑士团可就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  为娜娜莉而活的Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修是这么说的  玛丽安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊  他到底在想些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:41.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是Zero…是你开始的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修  我有话要对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Refrain
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华莲也知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它可以带我们回到令人怀念的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是一次的挫折  那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.67,0:12:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新考虑作战计划  挽回来不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟往常一样命令我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开Knight Mare？还是诱饵侦查？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我做什么都愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安慰我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是女人  没可能做不到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你是Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给了我们梦想  不是应该负责到底吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就一直骗下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要把完美的Zero…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演绎到底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任务是监视我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都差点忘了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系呢  忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽是痛苦和重负
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero也是  黑之骑士团也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  娜娜莉是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是为了娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero消失了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Area 11就能恢复和平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥只要变回普通学生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福地生活就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴望幸福有什么不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会伤害到任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在抛弃一切还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  只有我是哪里都不会去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:07.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远跟哥哥在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.65,0:14:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为何要申请
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出任Zero复活后的Area 11总督
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前一直在哥哥的保护中生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他现在行踪不明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.74,0:14:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他一定还在看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要做出  不会给哥哥丢脸的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很沉重哦  那副面具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅仅是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要有肩负世界的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是必须有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是布列塔尼亚军
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵舰的所属及航路  与申报有异
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请停船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在将进行强行临检
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:14:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将等待10分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:02.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前请所有乘员解除武装
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站到甲板上来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  大家都去修学旅行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要追上去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.04,0:15:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了  无人的鸟笼正适合现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁在…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路修也来放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭用剩的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  修学旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是就我们去了  你肯定会哭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键不是去哪里  而是跟谁一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说能实现愿望  所以做来试试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:16:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过怎么也想不起是跟谁学的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你许什么愿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经实现了哦  一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟大家一起放烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜  华莲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有鲁路修和罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:18.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只折了一只  所以只实现了鲁路的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得曾经跟娜娜莉和朱雀说过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果幸福是有形状的  会是什么样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是了  就像朱雀所说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许跟玻璃一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为平时不会察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它确实存在着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其证据就是  只要稍微改变观察的角度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻璃就会反映出光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:17:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比任何事物都更雄辩地论证自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说只要折一千只纸鹤  就能实现愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉想许什么愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望有个温馨的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温馨的世界就在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使被虚伪的记忆所沾污
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在透明的玻璃色彩里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直  永远  永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁路？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哭什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我们的友情所感动了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有可爱的一面嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是  怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再来这里一起放烟花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定  一定要再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.85,0:17:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:54.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不仅仅是为了娜娜莉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:17:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了  爆破油轮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让敌人的声纳失效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下潜30度  急速潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Zero的联络呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然中断
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该又是打算入海潜逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动Portman 2
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以被动无源定位确认
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.49,0:18:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从动力音判断应该是水中型
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降低深度  被发现就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.06,0:18:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反潜导弹  发射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用惊慌  只是盲攻而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.81,0:18:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以θ点为中心张开包围网
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人一定会慢慢被逼出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰内各部进水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.63,0:19:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤堂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦移动就会被对方捕捉到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:10.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Q-1  听得到吗  Q-1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下潜50度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向L14点急速潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.31,0:19:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶上来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  动作太慢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续投放深水炸弹  包围网不要散开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝正面发射全部鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定时雷管设为40秒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正面？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有敌人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了相信他还有其他办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设定雷管后  全弹发射
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认鱼雷发射音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到敌人位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人在点L14
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中攻击  浮上来后由我去捕获
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Salamander通告BlueDolphin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据定点改变发射角度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将Portman派往展开海域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网眼可是很细小的  别设错目标了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是Salamander  已经确认
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标设定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深水炸弹投射管  旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抛锚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员  准备承受冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空气？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  甲烷水合物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.59,0:20:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮力…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.62,0:20:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木卿  水沫…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水沫？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转舵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  要翻船了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从海底涌出的巨大水沫？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀  这不是派援军来就能解决的问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.66,0:21:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集合残存部队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把黑之骑士团…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero往这边来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的回答吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.91,0:21:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪的话就是违抗「君命」了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受娜娜莉总督的提议
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  就是日本特区的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是要投降吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.43,0:21:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.05,0:21:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.30,0:21:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero在此命令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:21:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑之骑士团全员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入  日本特区


